premise_source_doc_sentence: Mushroomhead is an American heavy metal band from Cleveland , Ohio .

Formed in 1993 in the Cleveland Warehouse District , the band is known for their avant-garde sound which includes influence from heavy metal , art rock and electro-industrial and their imagery which features masks and costumes as well as their unique live shows usually performed at smaller venues .
Mushroomhead has sold over 2 million units worldwide , and has made 8 studio albums and 15 music videos .
Over their lifetime , Mushroomhead has gone through many changes in band line-ups , with vocalist Jeffrey Hatrix and drummer Steve Felton being the only consistent members .
